    "LoadedMod holds Seq<LoadedMod> dependencies (self-referential graph)",
    "ModMeta is static inner class of Mods",
    "ModState is static inner enum of Mods",
    "ModLoadException extends RuntimeException",
    "ContentLoader references @Nullable LoadedMod currentMod (set during content registration)",
    "ContentParser references LoadedMod currentMod (set during parse)",
    "ContentParser holds ObjectMap<ContentType, TypeParser<?>> parsers (strategy per content type)",
    "ContentParser holds ObjectMap<Class<?>, FieldParser> classParsers (custom field deserialization)",
    "Scripts implements Disposable",
    "ContentLoader.createModContent() delegates to Mods.loadContent()",
    "Mods.loadContent() calls ContentParser.parse() per content file",
    "Mods.handleContentError() delegates to ContentParser.markError()",
    "Mods.addParseListener() injects into ContentParser.listeners"
  ],

  "loading_pipeline": [
    "1. Mods.load() — discovers .zip/.jar/folder mods, reads ModMeta via findMeta(), creates LoadedMod instances, resolves dependency order",
    "2. Mods.loadAsync() — packs mod sprites into TextureAtlas via MultiPacker (background thread)",
    "3. Mods.loadSync() — finalizes atlas, loads mod icons via loadIcons()",
    "4. Mods.loadScripts() — creates Scripts instance, iterates enabled mods, runs *.js files via scripts.run(mod, file)",
    "5. ContentLoader.createBaseContent() — loads all built-in content (Items, Blocks, Units, Liquids, Bullets, Planets...)",
    "6. ContentLoader.createModContent() → Mods.loadContent():",
    "   6a. For each Java mod: content.setCurrentMod(mod); mod.main.loadContent()",
    "   6b. Discovers content/*.json|hjson files per ContentType folder, respects contentOrder from ModMeta",
    "   6c. Calls ContentParser.parse(mod, name, json, file, type) → TypeParser.parse() → binds Content to ContentLoader via handleContent/handleMappableContent",
    "   6d. ContentParser.finishParsing() — runs deferred reads[], postreads[] to complete cross-referenced field population",
    "   6e. Events.fire(ModContentLoadEvent)",
    "7. ContentLoader.init() — calls Content.init() then Content.postInit() on all registered content",
    "8. ContentLoader.load() — calls Content.loadIcon() then Content.load() (client only)"
  ],

  "important_notes": [
    "Content registration is split: TypeParser binds the content object first (step 6c), field population is deferred to finishParsing() to allow cross-mod references.",
    "ContentLoader.setCurrentMod(LoadedMod) is called before and after each mod's content load to prefix names via transformName().",
    "ModState tracks per-mod status (enabled, contentErrors, missingDependencies, etc.); LoadedMod.enabled() returns true for both 'enabled' and 'contentErrors' states.",
    "Scripts are lazily instantiated; null until loadScripts() is called. Mods.hasScripts() checks for JS files before initializing Rhino.",
    "TypeParsers registered: block, unit, weather, liquid, status, sector, planet, team.",
    "ModClassLoader (extends ClassLoader) is used for JAR mods to isolate class loading.",
    "blacklistedMods is a static hardcoded ObjectSet<String> of known problematic mods.",
    "ContentParser.allowClassResolution and allowAssetLoading can be toggled for sandboxed/headless scenarios."
  ]
}
